# Enterprise AI Operations Copilot — Full Industry-Level LLMOps Project Blueprint

## Project Vision

Build a production-style AI Operations Assistant for engineering teams.

The platform should:

* Answer questions about infrastructure, codebases, logs, APIs, and deployments
* Investigate incidents automatically
* Search internal documentation using RAG
* Analyze metrics and logs
* Execute operational workflows through AI agents
* Include a complete enterprise-style LLMOps lifecycle

This is NOT a simple chatbot.

The goal is to simulate:

* AI SRE systems
* AI DevOps copilots
* Enterprise AI infrastructure assistants
* Agentic observability systems

